    <div class="container">

        <!-- Short Version -->
        <section id="short" class="short-version">
            <h2>The Short Version</h2>
            <p><strong>We collect:</strong> Account details, usage metrics, transaction history, and communications.</p>
            <p><strong>Why we use your data:</strong> To deliver, secure, personalize, and improve SkillSwap.</p>
            <p><strong>Sharing:</strong> Only with service providers, legal authorities (if required), or during business transfers. We never sell your personal data.</p>
            <p><strong>Your rights:</strong> Access, correct, delete, restrict processing, and withdraw consent at any time.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- 1. Introduction -->
        <section id="1">
            <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>SkillSwap (“we”, “us”) is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy describes how we collect, use, share, and secure your personal information when you use our website, mobile apps, and related services.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- 2. Information We Collect -->
        <section id="2">
            <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
            <h3>2.1 Account & Profile Data</h3>
            <p>Includes name, email, phone number, profile picture, bio, skills, and verification documents (ID/passport).</p>
            <h3>2.2 Usage & Technical Data</h3>
            <p>Pages visited, session duration, clicks, device/browser type, IP address, and approximate location.</p>
            <h3>2.3 Transactional Data</h3>
            <p>Token purchases, session bookings, payment method, billing address, and refund history.</p>
            <h3>2.4 Communications Data</h3>
            <p>Messages between users, support tickets, surveys, and feedback submissions.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- 3. Legal Basis -->
        <section id="3">
            <h2>3. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Consent:</strong> For marketing communications and optional features.</li>
                <li><strong>Contractual necessity:</strong> To perform services you’ve requested (e.g., booking, payments).</li>
                <li><strong>Legal obligation:</strong> To comply with laws (e.g., financial record-keeping).</li>
                <li><strong>Legitimate interests:</strong> To improve our services, ensure security, and prevent fraud.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- 4. Use of Information -->
        <section id="4">
            <h2>4. Use of Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use your data to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Match learners with tutors and enable session scheduling.</li>
                <li>Process token-based payments and handle refunds.</li>
                <li>Personalize recommendations and remember preferences.</li>
                <li>Analyze trends to improve platform performance.</li>
                <li>Detect fraud, enforce policies, and secure accounts.</li>
                <li>Communicate updates, alerts, and (with consent) marketing offers.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- 5. Sharing & Disclosure -->
        <section id="5">
            <h2>5. Sharing & Disclosure</h2>
            <p>We share data only when necessary:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Service providers:</strong> Hosting, payment processors, analytics partners bound by confidentiality.</li>
                <li><strong>Legal requests:</strong> In response to court orders, subpoenas, or regulatory inquiries.</li>
                <li><strong>Business transfers:</strong> During mergers or acquisitions, user data is one of the assets.</li>
                <li><strong>Public profile:</strong> Your username and profile details are visible on the platform.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- 6. Data Retention -->
        <section id="6">
            <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
            <p>We keep data only as long as needed:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Account data: Until deletion + 3 years.</li>
                <li>Transactional records: 7 years (tax and audit).</li>
                <li>Communications: 2 years.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- 7. Children’s Privacy -->
        <section id="7">
            <h2>7. Children’s Privacy</h2>
            <p>Our services are intended for users aged 16 and up. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children under 16. If you believe we have collected data from a child, please contact us to request deletion.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- 8. International Transfers -->
        <section id="8">
            <h2>8. International Data Transfers</h2>
            <p>Your data may be processed in countries outside your jurisdiction (e.g., India, USA). We use standard contractual clauses and other safeguards to protect your information.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- 9. Security Measures -->
        <section id="9">
            <h2>9. Security Measures</h2>
            <p>We implement technical and organizational safeguards—encryption in transit, access controls, and regular security audits—to protect your data from unauthorized access and breaches.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- 10. Your Rights -->
        <section id="10">
            <h2>10. Your Rights</h2>
            <p>You have the right to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Access and receive a copy of your data.</li>
                <li>Correct or complete inaccurate information.</li>
                <li>Delete your data, subject to legal obligations.</li>
                <li>Restrict or object to processing on legitimate interest grounds.</li>
                <li>Data portability: receive your data in a structured format.</li>
                <li>Withdraw consent for marketing at any time.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at privacy@skillswap.com.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- 11. Contact Us -->
        <section id="11">
            <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>Questions about this policy? Email  <a href="mailto:skillswap360@gmail.com">skillswap360@gmail.com</a>.</p>
        </section>

